# Methodological Decisions

During coding of the 2011 corpus, several methodological refinements were adopted.

### Included

* GAGAS Performance Audits
* Information Systems Performance Audits
* Official Audits Division Recommendation Follow-up Reviews (coded separately as Non-GAGAS Follow-up Reviews)

### Excluded

* Financial statement audits
* Contracted financial audits
* Comprehensive Annual Financial Reports (CAFRs)
* Financial Condition Reports
* Management Letters
* Enterprise fund financial reports
* Other financial reporting products lacking performance audit objectives

These decisions establish a stable inclusion protocol for subsequent years.

